"i sometimes find myself

191
00:11:41,984 --> 00:11:44,153
"admiring her
bright blue sky,

192
00:11:44,153 --> 00:11:46,322
"her grand old woods,

193
00:11:46,322 --> 00:11:47,406
"her fertile fields,

194
00:11:47,406 --> 00:11:50,659
"her beautiful rivers,
her mighty lakes

195
00:11:50,659 --> 00:11:53,379
and star-crowned
mountains..."

