the infernal spirit

199
00:12:02,054 --> 00:12:05,307
"of slaveholding
and wrong,

200
00:12:05,307 --> 00:12:09,095
"that with the waters
of her noblest rivers,

201
00:12:09,095 --> 00:12:10,730
"the tears
of my brethren

202
00:12:10,730 --> 00:12:12,898
"are borne to the ocean,

203
00:12:13,432 --> 00:12:16,152
