and forgotten,

204
00:12:16,152 --> 00:12:17,770
"that her
most fertile fields

205
00:12:17,770 --> 00:12:19,939
"drink daily
of the warm blood

206
00:12:19,939 --> 00:12:23,743
"of my outraged sisters,

207
00:12:23,743 --> 00:12:28,614
i am filled with
unutterable loathing."

208
00:12:28,614 --> 00:12:30,249
frederick douglass.

